@startuml
' lift_transcript: an a2a_pattern_* transcript becomes a protocol Trace, faithful to
' what the tool DID (it never invents steps). Palette: transcript=orange (task plane),
' lift=indigo, trace=slate, divergence=red.
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #e0e7ff
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #3730a3
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #fef9c3
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #a16207

start
#ffedd5:a2a_tasks.metadata.csm_transcript
[{round, role, output}, …];
:transcript_to_turns
(derive `converged` from a Reflector "CONVERGED");
:match ProtocolId;
split
  -[#3730a3]->
  :Sequential / Mixture / Distillation / Recursive
  → synthesize O→W:req . W→O:resp per turn;
split again
  -[#dc2626]->
  :Deliberation
  → on `converged`, emit O→R:reflect_req . R→O:converged
  then STOP (text impl omits the final O→T:finish.T→O:final);
  note right #fee2e2
    the lifted trace ends early ⇒ check_conformance
    reports Incomplete{T} — the real spec/impl
    divergence the observer exists to surface
  end note
split again
  -[#7c3aed]->
  :RecursiveCf
  → emit real comms (subcall/recurse/leaf/subresult);
  note right #ede9fe
    Call/Return boundaries are ε-moves taken
    by replay_to_configs ⇒ Dyck-balanced by
    construction
  end note
end split
#e2e8f0:Trace = Vec<Event>;
:replay_to_configs → check_conformance (ch.06);
stop
@enduml
